Package eu.acclimatize.unison.location

Contains classes for storing, obtaining, and deleting location data.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CoordinatesStore
    An interface that defines the contract between generic location classes and spatial database specific classes.
    LocationRepository
    An interface for a repository that stores LocationDetails information.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddLocationController
    A controller to add locations to be tracked.
    CoordinatesConfig
    A configuration class for CoordinatesStores.
    DeleteLocationController
    A controller to delete a location being tracked.
    GeoJsonSerializer
    Used by spatial database serializers to serialize point data to GeoJSON data.
    LocationController
    A controller to obtain an ordered list of location names and coordinates sorted by location name.
    LocationDetails
    An entity class for storing generic (non-spatial) information related to coordinates.
    ResponseConstant
    A class that defines response constants for adding and removing locations.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CoordinatesParseException
    A generic wrapper exception class for exceptions thrown when there is a problem parsing the coordinates for a spatial database.
